IMAPAccount coincoin
Host imaps.lautre.net
Port 993
User daffyduke@daffyduke.lautre.net
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.passwd/mutt.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS
#SSLVersions TLSv1.2
#UseIMAPS yes
#UseTLSv1 yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
DisableExtension COMPRESS=DEFLATE

IMAPStore coincoin-remote
Account coincoin

MaildirStore coincoin-local
Subfolders verbatim
Flatten .
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX

Channel coincoin-inbox
Far :coincoin-remote:
Near :coincoin-local:
Patterns * !"All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group coincoin
Channel coincoin-inbox
